-- Europe Defeats Britain and Ireland to Win Golf’s Seve Trophy
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2013-10-06T16:10:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-06/europe-defeats-britain-and-ireland-to-win-golf-s-seve-trophy.html
Continental Europe defeated Britain
and Ireland 15-13 for its first win in golf’s Seve Trophy
since the inaugural edition in 2000.  Italy’s Francesco Molinari clinched the victory by
defeating  England ’s Chris Wood 3 and 2 at Saint-Nom-la-Breteche,
 France .  Britain and Ireland were looking for a seventh straight win
in the two-yearly team event, named after five-time major winner
Severiano Ballesteros, who died in May 2011.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Christopher Elser  at   celser@bloomberg.net . 